title: What's a quinceañera anyway?
itunes:title: What's a quinceañera anyway?
description:
A quinceañera is the celebration of a girl of Hispanic heritage becoming a young woman on her 15th birthday. It involves family, friends, music and a lot of great food. Join Josh and Chuck as they don their favorite pink dresses and go over this wonderful tradition. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
